sing number of atomically thin 2D nanomaterials are being isolated, the\ngate-tunable p-n heterojunction concept presented here should be widely\ngeneralizable to realize diverse ultrathin, high-performance electronics and\noptoelectronics.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 22 Oct 2013 22:36:07 GMT"}],"update_date":"2013-10-24"}
